Package org.uclab.mm.kcl.edkat.dao

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ConclusionDAO
    This is Data Access Object interface for the conclusion this DAO provides interfaces to create, update, retrieve of conclusions of a specific rule
    ConditionDAO
    This is Data Access Object interface for the condition this DAO provides interfaces to create, update, retrieve of conditions of a specific rule
    RuleDAO
    This is Data Access Object class for the rule this DAO provides interfaces to create, update, retrieve of rules, conditions, conclusions, and situation
    SituationDAO
    This is interface for the situation this interface provides create, update, retrieve of situations of some specific rule
    UserDAO
    This is Data Access object interface for the user this DAO provides interface to create, update, retrieve of user
    WellnessConceptsModelDAO
    This is Data access object interface for the wellness model, it provides interfaces to create, update, retrieve of wellness concepts
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConclusionDAOImpl
    This is Data Access Object implementation class for the conclusion of a specific rule this DAO implementation handles to create, update, retrieve of conclusions of a particular rule
    ConditionDAOImpl
    This is Data Access Object implementation class for the condition this DAO provides implements to create, update, retrieve of conditions of a specific rule
    RuleDAOImpl
    This is Data Access Object implementation class for the rule this DAO implements to create, update, retrieve of rule with conditions, conclusions, and situations
    SituationDAOImpl
    This is interface for the situation this interface provides create, update, retrieve of situations of some specific rule
    UserDAOImpl
    This is Data Access Object implementation class for the user this DAO implements to create, update, retrieve of user information
    WellnessConceptsModelDAOImpl
    This is Data Access Object implementation class for the rule this DAO implements to create, update, retrieve of rule with conditions, conclusions, and situations
